bilingual.source: Look at the school noticeboards near the gate.
bilingual.target: 看看大门附近的学校公告板。

bilingual.source: The children went through the gate into the castle.
bilingual.target: 孩子们穿过大门进入城堡。

bilingual.source: I walked and walked along the street, and about 30 minutes later, I found myself at the school gate.
bilingual.target: 我在街上走啊走，大约半小时后我发现自己来到了学校大门口。

list.abstract: Gate（英 [ɡeɪt]，美 [ɡeɪt]），英语单词，作名词用，为门；围墙门；篱笆门。作动词用，为将…关在校内；不准…离校外出。短语搭配有at the gate（在大门口），例句为“Beside the gate of an ancient Roman city.（在一个古罗马城市的大门旁边）”。 Gate名词类近义词有portal、main entrance。
gate是一个英语单词，可以用作名词和及物动词，可以翻译为门、闸门，等等。

yingyinNormal.en: You will take the wall and open the gate to all China.
yingyinNormal.zh: 摧毁那座高耸的城墙就打开了通往中原的大门。

yingyinNormal.en: If we put the gate here, you'd be on a lane that links with the main road.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我们在这里建大门，正好小道是与主路相连的。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't know what you're up against. We don't let preggos or people with heart trouble past our front gate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不知道你的对手有多强大，我们不会让孕妇或者有心脏病的人经过我家大门。

yingyinNormal.en: Yesterday, we attempted to take the northeastern gate. Then we encountered from higher up and we're forced to pull back. We took heavy loses.
yingyinNormal.zh: 昨天我们试图拿下东北方向的大门，但我们在高处遭遇不测被迫撤回，我们损失惨重。

yingyinNormal.en: 400 miles away, deep in the heart to the Hunan Province is another epic holy site, but this time formed without human hands. A natural formation shaped by the area's unusual geology, Tian Men Shan, known as the heavens gate cave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 六百四十公里开外，在湖南省的腹地，坐落着另一个史诗级圣地，但是这回却并非出自人类手笔，而是大自然的鬼斧神工。天门山，也即通往天堂的大门。

yingyinNormal.en: Call everyone to the gate, to the gate, now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 叫所有人去前门，立刻去前门。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: Orc take prisoner for the gate. I learn from them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 献祭传送门的俘虏，我跟他们学的。

yingyinNormal.en: We're cutting budgets while the barbarians are at the gate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 敌人都打上门来了，还在削减预算。

yingyinNormal.en: The great gate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就是黑暗之门。

yingyinNormal.en: To feed the gate. To bring the Horde to take your world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了传送门需要的能量，然后整个部落都过来占领你们的世界。

yingyinNormal.en: Like wood for a fire. Green magic takes life to open the gate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 像木材用来生火一样，绿色魔法需要生命才能开门。

yingyinNormal.en: The great gate. Deep in ground and through magic brought us here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 黑暗之门，在地层深处，通过魔法把我们带到这儿来。

yingyinNormal.en: You're probably gonna catch her just as she's about to go to the gate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你应该会在登机门追上她。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, this is great. It's 5:00. My plane is now pulling away from the gate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是太棒了，现在已经五点了，我的飞机已经从登机口拖走了。

yingyinNormal.en: I will take back my words I rited at the gate. You did what only a true friend would do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我希望我能收回在城门上说过的话，只有真正的朋友才会像你这样。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: Right, you two, Wiggins has got your money by the gate, don't spend it all in one crack den.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们俩，去门口找威金斯拿钱，别都花在一个毒窟。

yingyinNormal.en: You ask anyone who survives a jump from the Golden Gate Bridge what their last thought is...
yingyinNormal.zh: 你去问问那些从金门大桥跳下来自杀的幸存者，他们最后的一刻的想法是什么…

yingyinNormal.en: The rebellion against Gul'dan is gaining strength. With their help we can destroy this gate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 反对古尔丹的叛乱正在发展壮大，有了他们的帮助，我们可以摧毁这个门。

yingyinNormal.en: It's actually secret option number three, you meet her at the gate. That way she knows you love her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实是第三个秘密绝招你在登机门与她碰面，这就表现出你对她的爱。

yingyinNormal.en: What? You're walking up to her at the gate? Have you never chased anyone through the airport before?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你就直接去登机口？以前在没在机场追过人？
